---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Aditya's About"
  seoTitle="About Aditya, Software Engineer"
  seoDesc={"Hi there! My name is Aditya, and I'm a software engineer " +
    "and data analyst."}
>
  <div class="w-6/12 mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-5xl">About</h1>
    <img
      src="/public/images/about.jpg"
      class="my-2 shadow-md drop-shadow-[10px_10px_35px_rgba(39,245,131,0.6)]"
    />
    <p>
      Yo! My name is Aditya, and I'm a software engineer and data analyst. I'm passionate about building
      high-quality software that solves real-world problems and makes people's
      lives easier and analyse data to extract meaningful insights.
    </p><br />
    <p>
      My expertise lies in full-stack development, with a focus on web
      applications and data analysis using python and its libraries. I'm proficient in a variety of programming languages,
      including JavaScript, Python, and R, and I'm comfortable working with
      tools and frameworks like React, Node.js, Django, Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn, TensorFlow, PyTorch, and many more.
    </p><br />
    <p>
      In addition to my technical skills, I pride myself on my ability to
      collaborate with team members and communicate effectively with
      stakeholders. I'm a better observer and natural problem solver and enjoy tackling complex
      challenges and come up with solutions whether it is in software development or data analysis or anything.
    </p><br />
    <p>
      When I'm not coding, you can find me stone crafting, playing
      chess or fishing beside the river. I'm always looking for new opportunities to work
      on exciting projects, so if you're interested in collaborating, please
      feel free to get in touch. Thanks for stopping by!
    </p>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
